Class SymbolWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cyc.kb.wrapper.KbObjectWrapper
      • com.cyc.kb.wrapper.SymbolWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    KbObject, Symbol

    public abstract class SymbolWrapper
extends KbObjectWrapper
implements Symbol
    An abstract base class for implementing Symbols per the decorator pattern. To use, extend this class and implement the wrapped() method to return the wrapped object.
